{"tid":2130341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"岑子杰遇襲案 被告指屯門有港人出二百萬「打跛阿杰隻腳」","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T11:26:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":335,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"ab94d65fd83ac061c70b0f8a4b170cf57d21950b","tid":2130341,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/VNTOG6N3FWATO4TIDXKXLIB7KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FVNTOG6N3FWATO4TIDXKXLIB7KU%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6dagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=55ae18c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FVNTOG6N3FWATO4TIDXKXLIB7KU%2F&h=7d296bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/VNTOG6N3FWATO4TIDXKXLIB7KU/</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰去年在佐敦與友人午膳期間，遭兩名蒙面南亞裔男子持棒球棍及牛肉刀闖入餐廳襲擊，友人用手擋棍時受傷。警方拘控曾駕車接載施襲者的兩名男子，其中一人年僅15歲。案件今續審，有認罪的被告向警方透露，早於襲擊案前半個月，已有印度男子向他表示會襲擊「阿杰」，更稱施襲原因是「屯門有香港人要打跛阿杰隻腳，酬勞有二百萬」。"},{"pid":"b5a3a1fb1fac932c8de97749874e0fb5fa9b73f8","tid":2130341,"uid":88743,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"何已完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b115ec2235fb02ce8c0aa9bdc67e5eb75eff9202","tid":2130341,"uid":77196,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:28.000Z","msg":"姓何? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18aaac2e515e0a630c776e49ad09dceeeb6d3bc2","tid":2130341,"uid":127929,"like":130,"dislike":0,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"出錢個個係咪姓何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫君堯?"},{"pid":"d6aea73618d1c76e29f4a2d3b01f47d0c72aa48e","tid":2130341,"uid":321059,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"屯門<br />\n何已完？<img src=\"/assets